data.description: Welcome to this cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bath home that has been well taken care of by the current owners. It's the perfect starter home with quick access to I-145 and I-20, only 15 minutes from Downtown Dallas. Home features a huge backyard with plenty of room for outdoor family activity and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours. Buyers and their agents are encouraged to verify all information and measurements to ensure complete satisfaction.
